title: Choy Ma's Kitchen
description: Vegetarian restaurant located in Green Bamboo organic shop in the heart of the city. Try the steamboat that comes with 6 sauces. Also serves various noodle dishes. On the 1st and 15th day of each month offers additional food such as yong tau fu, chicken rice, andherbal tea dish with rice.
streetAddress: 36 A Jalan Desa Bakti, Faber Plaza, Taman Desa
